| Criterion | How PitchTwin addresses it |
|---|---|
| Functional Product (20pts) | End-to-end happy path: profile → proposal → twin chat → debrief |
| Multi-Agent Architecture (20pts) | 7 specialized agents, clear roles, parallel + sequential orchestration, explicit handoffs |
| Agentic SDLC (10pts) | spec.plan + spec.tasks + spec.arch drive the build |
| Architect's Blueprint (10pts) | This document |
| Impact (5pts) | Internal: saves consultant time. Market: SaaS-ready pattern for any firm |
| Presentation (10pts) | Clear problem→solution→demo arc |
